## Limitations

The primary limitation of this report is the reliance on secondary sources, which may not capture the latest scientific research or emerging trends in climate science. Additionally, the data is limited to the information available up to October 2023, and newer studies or findings may not be included. Furthermore, while the sources used are reputable, the complexity of climate systems means that there are still uncertainties and ongoing debates within the scientific community regarding specific aspects of climate change.

